    <abstract>
      <t>The Label Distribution Protocol (LDP) specification defines procedures to exchange label bindings over either IPv4, or IPv6 or both networks. This document corrects and clarifies the LDP behavior when IPv6 network is used (with or without IPv4). This document updates RFC 5036 and RFC 6720.</t>
